<bibRefCitation author="Rolston, L. H." box="[1105,1292,367,394]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" pagination="1 - 47" refId="ref63613" refString="Rolston, L. H. (1983 b) A revision of the genus Lincus Stal (Hemiptera: Pentatomidae: Discocephalinae: Ochlerini). New York Entomological Society, 91, 1 - 47." type="journal article" year="1983">Rolston (1983b)</bibRefCitation>
